A great slip-on shoe from vans, so comfortable, practical and durable you'll want to wear it every day. With a conservatively striped upper, this slip on will coordinate with all your outfits, and the striped lining gives this shoe a little stylish lift.

Brand name on the back, on the lasting

Outsole

name: Flying Machine Men Grey Casual Shoes
description:
These flying machine shoes are inspired by a retro-esque fusion of fashion with contemporary styles. Iconic and synonymous with style in the youth culture, these shoes reflect a fusion of sport and style. Sleek silhouetting on this canvas shoe make this an off-duty essential. Cut a dash to all off-duty dos with these throwback classic canvas shoes. Wear this with form fitting denims, a monochrome tee and a casual jacket.

Upper
denim upper for style, easy maintenance and durability
Central lacing for a snug Fit
PU toe box for enhanced protection of the upper foot
Long canvas tongue for added comfort and snug fit
Lace-ups through metal eyelets for snug fit and durability

Midsole
PU midsole for impact protection

Outsole
Vulcanized rubber outsole for flexibility and traction
Brick and herringbone patterned grooves on the outsole

Slipper care
Make a paste using 1 tbsp of baking soda, 1 tbsp white vinegar and 1 tbsp hot water
Rub this paste onto the canvas and the sole using a brush
Wash off with lukewarm water
